%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Manager
    participant UI as Project Dashboard
    participant API as Project API
    participant DB as Database
    participant Notify as Notifications

    Manager->>UI: Create project
    UI->>API: POST /api/projects {name, key, description}
    API->>DB: Check key uniqueness
    alt Key Exists
        API-->>UI: Error: Project key taken
    else Key Available
        API->>DB: INSERT project
        API->>DB: Create default columns (Todo, In Progress, Review, Done)
        API->>DB: Set WIP limits per column
        API-->>UI: Project created
    end

    Manager->>UI: Add team members
    UI->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/members {userIds[], role}
    par For each user
        API->>DB: Link user to project
        API->>Notify: Send project invite
    end
    API-->>UI: Members added

    Manager->>UI: Create milestone
    UI->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/milestones {name, targetDate}
    API->>DB: INSERT milestone
    API-->>UI: Milestone created

    Manager->>UI: Link tasks to milestone
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/tasks/{id} {milestoneId}
    API->>DB: UPDATE task.milestoneId
    API-->>UI: Task linked

    UI->>API: GET /api/milestones/{id}/progress
    API->>DB: Count tasks (completed vs total)
    DB-->>API: {completed: 8, total: 12}
    API-->>UI: 66.7% complete

    alt Progress < 50% AND Deadline < 7 days
        API->>Notify: Alert: Milestone at risk
        Notify-->>Manager: Email + push notification
    end
